events were cancelled because the water was too dirty, as were the swimming legs on two of the four days of triathlon and para-triathlon tests.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the marathon swimming test events\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"the swimming legs\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 805}, {\"ngram\": \"the four days\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"triathlon\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"para-triathlon tests\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers have insisted \\\"there is no Plan B\\\" but the Brazilian called for a rethink.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 880}, {\"ngram\": \"no Plan B\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brazilian\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 933}, {\"ngram\": \"a rethink\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a concern,\\\" Cunha said on the sidelines of a competition on Rio de Janeiro's Copacabana beach.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euclides_da_Cunha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.862311589824305e-15, \"text\": \"Cunha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euclides_da_Cunha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euclides_da_Cunha\"}, {\"begin\": 1023, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0767578206043256e-19, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a concern\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"the sidelines\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"a competition\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was no test event last year because of this but (the organisers) insist on wanting the events to take place there.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no test event\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"(the organisers\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1159}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need a Plan B in case it's not possible to swim in the Seine,\\\" she said, adding that difficulties in swimming in Paris were linked to an \\\"infrastructure\\\" problem.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1241, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2547177331910666e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.661190314214784e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a Plan B\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1199}, {\"ngram\": \"case\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulties\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1283}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"infrastructure\\\" problem\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Seine is not made for swimming,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2547177331910666e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1385}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The organisers have deliberately chosen a route for the men and women's 10km events that will showcase the beauty of the city.\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organisers\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"a route\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"the men\", \"from\": 1451, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"women's 10km events\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1482}, {\"ngram\": \"the beauty\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Cunha, 31, believes that is secondary to the health of the athletes.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euclides_da_Cunha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.862311589824305e-15, \"text\": \"Cunha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euclides_da_Cunha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Euclides_da_Cunha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the health\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1582}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not a question of erasing the history of the Seine,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2547177331910666e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a question\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We know what the Pont Alexandre-III and the Eiffel Tower represent but I think that the health of the athletes must come first.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Pont Alexandre-III\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1706}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"the health\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The organisers must accept that perhaps it will, unfortunately, not be possible to hold the events where they want to.\\\"\", \"from\": 1800, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The organisers\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With less than five months to go before the opening ceremony on July 26, the water quality of the Seine continues to give organisers sleepless nights.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2020, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.2547177331910666e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"less than five months\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"the water quality\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"sleepless nights\", \"from\": 2055, \"to\": 2071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French authorities have spent \\u20ac1.4 billion (S$2 billion) upgrading sewage and storm water treatment facilities in the Paris region to improve the water quality of the Seine as well as its major tributary, the Marne.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2074, \